method.description:

Generates the signature file. 

<p>In order to generate the signature, the <a href='type://Signature#getToSign() file to sign'>#getToSign() file to sign</a>, <a href='type://Signature#getSignatory() signatory'>#getSignatory() signatory</a> and <a href='type://Signature#getSignatureType() signature type'>#getSignatureType() signature type</a> must be known (i.e. non <a href='type://null'>null</a>).</p> 

@throws InvalidUserDataException if the there is insufficient information available to generate the signature.
